President Muhammadu Buhari is currently meeting with Antony Blinken, the United States secretary of state, at the presidential villa, Abuja. The US top diplomatâ€™s motorcade drove into the presidential complex at about 3.47pm on Thursday for a meeting with the president. After the meeting, Blinken is expected to proceed to the office of Vice President Yemi Osinbajo where some agreements between Nigeria and the US will be signed. Blinken will subsequently hold a joint press conference with Geoffrey Onyeama, minister of foreign affairs, before departing the presidential villa. See photos from the meeting below. <img class="alignnone wp-image-630305" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="673" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4.jpg 892w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4-268x300.jpg 268w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4-768x861.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4-21x24.jpg 21w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4-32x36.jpg 32w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken4-43x48.jpg 43w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /> <img class="alignnone wp-image-630309" src="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="526" srcset="https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken.jpg 1140w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken-300x263.jpg 300w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken-1024x898.jpg 1024w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken-768x674.jpg 768w, https://f5p3e9e4.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Buhari-Blinken-24x21.jp